  m_Name: Dlg_Tutorial_AfterShovel
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - "The last element is the most exciting one \u2014 fire."
  - You have a fine furnace in your lab, but it needs to be lit.
  - Gather some wood to throw in. Three branches should be enough.
